PayloadJson.description:
操作参数（JSON 字符串）。

add_variable 示例：{"name": "Health", "type": {"category": "float"}, "defaultValue": "100.0", "category": "Stats", "tooltip": "Player health", "instanceEditable": true, "exposeOnSpawn": false, "replicated": false}

remove_variable 示例：{"name": "OldVariable"}

modify_variable 示例：{"name": "Health", "defaultValue": "150.0", "category": "Updated Stats"}
